OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1773497486
OL,3,CSeventh dog found after thieves steal
OL,4,Cdog walker's van
OL,6,FAll seven dogs taken from a stolen van
OL,7,Fin the Oldham area have now been
OL,8,Frecovered.
OL,10,FShortly after 11am on 10 March, a van
OL,11,Fowned by a dog walking business was
OL,12,Ftaken from Medlock Road, Failsworth.
OL,14,FThe stolen vehicle made off at speed
OL,15,Fbut the dogs were dumped in the
OL,16,FAlexandra Park area and the van was
OL,17,Fabandoned.
OL,19,FWhile the majority of the dogs were
OL,20,Frecovered soon after, one of the dogs
OL,21,Fremained missing.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
