OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1773497486
OL,3,CSeventh dog found after thieves steal
OL,4,Cdog walker's van
OL,6,FOver the last couple of days,
OL,7,Fvolunteers including a retired Oldham
OL,8,Fneighbourhood officer, Huddersfield
OL,9,FCanine Search & Rescue, and Oldham
OL,10,FPCSOs have helped track the dog, with
OL,11,Fseveral sightings being reported by
OL,12,Fmembers of the public.
OL,14,FThe dog was finally found in an
OL,15,Fovergrown area, with the help of
OL,16,Fthermal imaging and the dog's owner.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1773497486
OL,3,CSeventh dog found after thieves steal
OL,4,Cdog walker's van
OL,6,FSergeant Zahid Iqbal, from GMP's
OL,7,FOldham Neighbourhood Team, said: "The
OL,8,Finitial theft of the car containing
OL,9,Fthe seven dogs was an incredibly
OL,10,Fupsetting incident for the pet owners,
OL,11,Fand one we are continuing to
OL,12,Finvestigate.
OL,14,F"I am glad that our local team have
OL,15,Fmanaged to work very effectively
OL,16,Ftogether with local volunteers and
OL,17,Fgroups to find all of the dogs ` it is
OL,18,Fdefinitely a positive result.
OL,26,@oD@bOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1773497486
OL,3,CSeventh dog found after thieves steal
OL,4,Cdog walker's van
OL,6,F"Of course, however, we are
OL,7,Finvestigating the full circumstances
OL,8,Fof the van theft and are undertaking
OL,9,Fmultiple enquiries as part of this
OL,10,Fwork."
OL,12,FKirstie Hobson, from Huddersfield
OL,13,FCanine Search & Rescue, said: "The
OL,14,Ffeedback and Facebook comments have
OL,15,Fbeen amazing. The local PCSOs have
OL,16,Fbeen supporting the searches
OL,17,Fthroughout and by combining our
OL,18,Fefforts, we have thankfully now
OL,19,Frecovered the final missing dog."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@FO]uD@_OU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1773497486
OL,3,CSeventh dog found after thieves steal
OL,4,Cdog walker's van
OL,6,F"The families of the dogs have been so
OL,7,Fresilient during such an awful
OL,8,Fsituation and we were very happy to
OL,9,Fsupport wherever we could. It has been
OL,10,Fa real team effort from everyone from
OL,11,Four group - including lots of work
OL,12,Fbehind the scenes."
OL,14,FAnyone with information are urged to
OL,15,Fcontact Greater Manchester Police,
OL,16,Fparticularly with CCTV, dashcam, or
OL,17,Fdoorbell footage from the area.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
